Terres de Paroles, the traveling literary festival in Seine-Maritime, which runs from Saturday September 30 to Sunday October 8, 2023, accompanies the national release of the film YOLO, ON N?A QU?UNE VIE, directed and produced by Collectif Art Vif.

? Synopsis:
